of that power.

00:04:11.542 --> 00:04:14.521
The whole world is created out of that power.

00:04:14.521 --> 00:04:23.292
In everything that power resides and works
out, sorts out, co-ordinates things for us.

00:04:23.292 --> 00:04:26.071
