00:48:10.992 --> 00:48:14.072
Yes, please - little loudly....can you say
loudly, please?

00:48:14.072 --> 00:48:23.782
Q. Why is the picture sitting on the table
lying next to you?

00:48:23.782 --> 00:48:28.252
Shri Mataji: Why?

00:48:28.252 --> 00:48:31.442
You don't like it?

00:48:31.442 --> 00:48:40.572
It's a question really something I can't understand.

00:48:40.572 --> 00:48:47.142
You see, if I am something, if this picture
is My true picture, then why not have it?

00:48:47.142 --> 00:48:49.524
All the pictures you have of Christ are not
His own.

00:48:49.524 --> 00:48:56.572
Very few people have seen Him and also there
is no one who has taken His picture.

00:48:56.572 --> 00:48:59.422
Actually, when I see the pictures of Christ
I get a shock.

00:48:59.422 --> 00:49:01.201
I said, "How can this be Christ?"

00:49:01.201 --> 00:49:06.042
I mean, this miserable creature cannot be
Christ at all, but you don't mind having all

00:49:06.042 --> 00:49:07.052
these things around.

00:49:07.052 --> 00:49:13.022
Even the cross that you have can be horrible,
made of plastic, made of this, made of that.

00:49:13.022 --> 00:49:15.682
That gives horrible vibrations to you.

00:49:15.682 --> 00:49:17.471
You don't know anything about it.

00:49:17.471 --> 00:49:23.902
With this picture, you'll be surprised, the
person who first got realization got through

00:49:23.902 --> 00:49:24.902
this picture.

00:49:24.902 --> 00:49:26.792
In this picture there are vibrations.

00:49:26.792 --> 00:49:30.642
When you will get realized, you will know
that only this picture has that vibration

00:49:30.642 --> 00:49:34.951
because the real thing it is - thank God that
science has given us the real thing.

00:49:34.951 --> 00:49:40.612
If there were cameras before, we would have
had pictures of all those great people.

00:49:40.612 --> 00:49:43.242
Because there were no photographs they said,
"Better not have any pictures."

00:49:43.242 --> 00:49:48.752
Because all the pictures were imaginary, done
by people who wanted to have some money.

00:49:48.752 --> 00:49:53.762
With this picture, many people have been cured.

00:49:53.762 --> 00:49:55.902
All right?

00:49:55.902 --> 00:49:58.242
Especially in Australia, a miracle happened.

00:49:58.242 --> 00:50:00.572
That's how media took me over.

00:50:00.572 --> 00:50:08.332
There was a lady, a friend of a very big journalist
and a businessman there who was in coma and

00:50:08.332 --> 00:50:15.332
doctors said she has got a brain trouble and
she cannot come back to her normal condition.

00:50:15.332 --> 00:50:19.532
There is a damage in her brain and she is
dying.

00:50:19.532 --> 00:50:23.072
Then everybody had given up hopes and there
was one Sahaja Yogini and she said, "All right,

00:50:23.072 --> 00:50:25.742
you just allow me to put this photograph under
her pillow."

00:50:25.742 --> 00:50:28.302
And you'll be surprised: she came to consciousness
next day.

00:50:28.302 --> 00:50:31.002
By the time I reached there, she was very
conscious.

00:50:31.002 --> 00:50:34.052
So all the media was there to receive me in
Australia.

00:50:34.052 --> 00:50:38.632
I was surprised because media is the last
which attends to anything that is real.

00:50:38.632 --> 00:50:42.662
I was Myself aghast to see them there.

00:50:42.662 --> 00:50:46.802
But it's one thing, no doubt, and it's really
true and it happened and now that woman is

00:50:46.802 --> 00:50:47.802
walking about.

00:50:47.802 --> 00:50:49.942
You can write to her and find out.

00:50:49.942 --> 00:50:53.592
So this is what it is.

00:50:53.592 --> 00:50:58.002
It's a very good thing that has happened that
we can take pictures now because I think,

00:50:58.002 --> 00:51:06.962
I cannot meet everyone in this world but they
can at least see my picture.

00:51:06.962 --> 00:51:08.972
People get cured by this picture.

00:51:08.972 --> 00:51:09.972
What's wrong?

00:51:09.972 --> 00:51:12.752
Supposing your picture was like that, I would
like to put it there.

00:51:12.752 --> 00:51:14.721
But is it like that?

00:51:14.721 --> 00:51:15.721
That's the point.

00:51:15.721 --> 00:51:17.392
You see some people say, "Why you are doing
it?"

00:51:17.392 --> 00:51:18.582
I say, "Better you do it.

00:51:18.582 --> 00:51:19.772
I would like to retire."

00:51:19.772 --> 00:51:21.912
Actually, today my husband was very angry
with me.

00:51:21.912 --> 00:51:23.812
He said, "Why are you there on Saturdays?

00:51:23.812 --> 00:51:24.812
Why don't you come?"

00:51:24.812 --> 00:51:27.232
I said, "Now it has been advertised too much.

00:51:27.232 --> 00:51:28.602
I just can't come."

00:51:28.602 --> 00:51:32.092
He is not, he wants me there for some purpose
and he was not very happy about it.

00:51:32.092 --> 00:51:35.432
So I would be very happy if you could sit
down here and do the job.

00:51:35.432 --> 00:51:36.432
You see, I'll be very happy.

00:51:36.432 --> 00:51:37.432
I'll retire.

00:51:37.432 --> 00:51:38.432
But you can't do it.

00:51:38.432 --> 00:51:41.742
And why to feel bad if I can do it?

00:51:41.742 --> 00:51:44.272
Because you can do many more things that I
cannot.

00:51:44.272 --> 00:51:49.622
For example, I can't drive, I don't know how
to write a check, I don't know anything that

00:51:49.622 --> 00:51:50.622
you know.

00:51:50.622 --> 00:51:51.932
So many things there are that I do not know.

00:51:51.932 --> 00:51:52.932
You'll be amazed.

00:51:52.932 --> 00:51:57.992
I am so simple that people can call me a rustic
woman because I don't know many things that

00:51:57.992 --> 00:51:59.152
you know.

00:51:59.152 --> 00:52:04.062
But I know one thing: that is awakening of
your Kundalini, and then another thing is

00:52:04.062 --> 00:52:17.451
that this photograph also knows you somehow.

00:52:17.451 --> 00:52:22.451
Yes please?

00:52:22.451 --> 00:52:33.632
Q; How did you discover such a quick way of
self realization?

00:52:33.632 --> 00:52:38.442
Shri Mataji: Must be something about Me, sir.

00:52:38.442 --> 00:52:40.082
You better find out.

00:52:40.082 --> 00:52:41.082
It's true.

00:52:41.082 --> 00:52:42.082
It's true.

00:52:42.082 --> 00:52:44.221
But something about Me, definitely.

00:52:44.221 --> 00:52:47.992
You see, whatever our education is, you have
come to us with wisdom and all that, it has

00:52:47.992 --> 00:52:51.692
come to us through other English writers and
western writers.

00:52:51.692 --> 00:52:58.221
But if you really go into the literature,
you will know that it is already prophesized.

00:52:58.221 --> 00:53:01.702
Even William Blake has prophesized absolutely
about Sahaja Yoga.

00:53:01.702 --> 00:53:07.132
He said that God of men [men of god?] will
become prophets and they will have powers

00:53:07.132 --> 00:53:09.412
to make others prophets.

00:53:09.412 --> 00:53:11.692
But who reads Blake?

00:53:11.692 --> 00:53:13.972
No one;they read Freud.

00:53:13.972 --> 00:53:20.191
He's described to such a detail about Sahaja
Yoga that sometimes I am amazed.

00:53:20.191 --> 00:53:24.952
No Indian seer has seen that what William
Blake has seen.

00:53:24.952 --> 00:53:32.362
But our mentality is funny because once he
had his exhibition; I went to see his exhibition

00:53:32.362 --> 00:53:35.032
and people were looking at nude women that
he had painted.

00:53:35.032 --> 00:53:36.032
He was innocent.

00:53:36.032 --> 00:53:40.922
He didn't paint any nudity; he just painted
women without any dress, just the body.

00:53:40.922 --> 00:53:43.582
But they were looking at the nude women.

00:53:43.582 --> 00:53:45.481
So, look at our mentality.

00:53:45.481 --> 00:53:53.132
Looking at William Blake also we praise him
because he has painted women without dress.

00:53:53.132 --> 00:53:54.662
He was innocent.

00:53:54.662 --> 00:53:55.662
It has to be done.

00:53:55.662 --> 00:53:57.772
The time has come.

00:53:57.772 --> 00:54:02.721
At the beginning of life, I know there were
hardly one or two people, but today is the

00:54:02.721 --> 00:54:07.112
time, a time where many have to become.

00:54:07.112 --> 00:54:11.912
As you know, on the tree of life there were
few flowers.

00:54:11.912 --> 00:54:18.092
Now there has to be many flowers because the
blossom time has come and it has to be simple.

00:54:18.092 --> 00:54:22.951
But supposing it is simple, must you not accept?

00:54:22.951 --> 00:54:26.711
It's like my grandmother saying, "I don't
believe you can go to moon.

00:54:26.711 --> 00:54:29.052
How can it be possible?"

00:54:29.052 --> 00:54:30.451
It's like that.

00:54:30.451 --> 00:54:32.332
It's a jet age.

00:54:32.332 --> 00:54:35.912
If there is speed outside, if the tree is
growing outside too much, something must have

00:54:35.912 --> 00:54:38.981
grown inside: the roots.

00:54:38.981 --> 00:54:43.481
And this is the knowledge of the roots which
you do not know, which you should know, how

00:54:43.481 --> 00:54:47.322
it has grown, what it is sucking.

00:54:47.322 --> 00:54:48.422
All right?

00:54:48.422 --> 00:54:50.242
If it is so, why not have it?

00:54:50.242 --> 00:54:53.492
I mean, if I say there's a diamond, will you
refuse it?

00:54:53.492 --> 00:54:56.201
You'll say, "All right, if it's diamond then
let us see."

00:54:56.201 --> 00:55:03.342
It's more than all the diamonds put together.

00:55:03.342 --> 00:55:05.532
It's true.

00:55:05.532 --> 00:55:14.542
It is very simple to understand if you see
God's point of view.

00:55:14.542 --> 00:55:17.792
This creation has to have a meaning.

00:55:17.792 --> 00:55:19.172
And you are going to give it the meaning.

00:55:19.172 --> 00:55:23.842
If it doesn't work out, this creation, it
is going to destroy, because human beings

00:55:23.842 --> 00:55:27.342
are going to be destroyed.

00:55:27.342 --> 00:55:29.022
You can see that.

00:55:29.022 --> 00:55:37.662
You can see around what is the situation is.

00:55:37.662 --> 00:56:25.742
Q: [Unclear Side B 22:57]
Shri Mataji: It's a little confused question

00:56:25.742 --> 00:56:33.062
because, you see... but I understand what
you are trying to say, that people are seeing

00:56:33.062 --> 00:56:36.242
it through now because they are intelligent.

00:56:36.242 --> 00:56:39.461
They are seeing through and it has reached
a certain culminating point, you see.

00:56:39.461 --> 00:56:45.431
All these philosophies have reached certain
culminating point and they are seeing that,

00:56:45.431 --> 00:56:46.431
what is the result.

00:56:46.431 --> 00:56:50.252
Now the time has come for them to see the
result of all their mental projections we

00:56:50.252 --> 00:56:51.862
have had about everything.

00:56:51.862 --> 00:56:54.951
So people are thinking that there must be
an answer to all this.

00:56:54.951 --> 00:56:59.262
Whatever we have done may have been little
wrong or something has been more linear.

00:56:59.262 --> 00:57:03.912
It is not expanding us and it is not giving
us what was promised to us.

00:57:03.912 --> 00:57:07.492
So they are thinking about it and they are
going down to find out the answers.

00:57:07.492 --> 00:57:09.272
That's why there is a seeking, no doubt.

00:57:09.272 --> 00:57:15.342
But it is also the plan that they should be
here, that they should be on this earth at

00:57:15.342 --> 00:57:16.342
this time.

00:57:16.342 --> 00:57:17.451
All, so many things have worked out.

00:57:17.451 --> 00:57:20.762
But the reason is that there is confusion
today.

00:57:20.762 --> 00:57:23.262
In this confusion only, you are going to find
it out.

00:57:23.262 --> 00:57:27.961
If you were not confused, if you were sure
that you are doing the right thing and you

00:57:27.961 --> 00:57:32.352
have done whatever is right which was before
this, then you would not have thought of it.

00:57:32.352 --> 00:57:37.912
But just now people are seeing that we are
relatively living: "This is also right.

00:57:37.912 --> 00:57:38.912
This is also right."

00:57:38.912 --> 00:57:39.912
How can that be?

00:57:39.912 --> 00:57:40.912
If right is one then it should be one.

00:57:40.912 --> 00:57:42.572
So people are thinking about it.

00:57:42.572 --> 00:57:43.572
They are seeking.

00:57:43.572 --> 00:57:45.282
In this seeking they might do mistakes.

00:57:45.282 --> 00:57:51.582
And people might do many mistakes like going
to wrong gurus, might spend money for it,

00:57:51.582 --> 00:57:55.731
may become bankrupts, might go to drugs, might
do this punk rock... all kinds of things.

00:57:55.731 --> 00:58:02.711
They are nothing but expression of that feeling
within that there is something beyond.

00:58:02.711 --> 00:58:07.342
It's true that this confusion has led to this
seeking.

00:58:07.342 --> 00:58:08.872
No doubt about it.

00:58:08.872 --> 00:58:10.112
Because they are all challenged.

00:58:10.112 --> 00:58:11.112
These philosophies are challenged.

00:58:11.112 --> 00:58:12.112
Everything is challenged.

00:58:12.112 --> 00:58:15.322
And people see that it has given no result.

00:58:15.322 --> 00:58:17.412
Our forefathers did the same; we are doing
the same.

00:58:17.412 --> 00:58:18.461
What's the use?

00:58:18.461 --> 00:58:20.471
We have to reach somewhere.

00:58:20.471 --> 00:58:26.512
For example, Jung has talked of universal
unconsciousness much before I came.

00:58:26.512 --> 00:58:30.951
They have prepared the stage for Sahaja Yoga,
I should say.

00:58:30.951 --> 00:58:33.451
All right?

00:58:33.451 --> 00:58:40.941
Q: [Unclear : something about another guru...

00:58:40.941 --> 00:58:44.681
Side B 25:51].

00:58:44.681 --> 00:58:50.902
Shri Mataji: Oh, now don't ask about them.

00:58:50.902 --> 00:58:53.092
What do you think about him?

00:58:53.092 --> 00:58:55.352
What have they done?

00:58:55.352 --> 00:59:00.492
What good have they done to you?

00:59:00.492 --> 00:59:08.242
In general, there is one principle you must
apply to all of them.

00:59:08.242 --> 00:59:14.782
On the gross, anybody who is interested in
your money is not your guru; he is a parasite,

00:59:14.782 --> 00:59:15.921
on the gross.

00:59:15.921 --> 00:59:25.642
In the subtle, anybody who doesn't manifest
your powers has no powers of his own.

00:59:25.642 --> 00:59:28.481
These two you apply to every guru and don't
ask Me individual question.

00:59:28.481 --> 00:59:46.332
The one who is interested in Rolls Royce,
I mean if you think him to be a guru, I must

00:59:46.332 --> 00:59:49.543
say this is something surprising.

00:59:49.543 --> 00:59:50.543
Very surprising.

00:59:50.543 --> 00:59:51.543
It's a [not clear: sounds like paras attitude
Side B 26:52]

00:59:51.543 --> 01:00:32.092
Yes, he can... [probably Mother permitting
someone from the audience to ask a question]

01:00:32.092 --> 01:00:33.992
Q:[unclear question.

01:00:33.992 --> 01:00:39.312
Sounds like: I wonder whether you have anything
in your faith which corresponds to the Apostles?

01:00:39.312 --> 01:00:40.312
In the Scriptures?

01:00:40.312 --> 01:00:41.312
Do you have any Apostles?

01:00:41.312 --> 01:00:42.312
Side B 27:46]
Shri Mataji:.

01:00:42.312 --> 01:00:43.312
It's again confused, my child, but doesn't
matter.

01:00:43.312 --> 01:00:45.052
Let's see now...they had a hot air on their
head.

01:00:45.052 --> 01:00:46.382
Did you say so?

01:00:46.382 --> 01:00:47.542
When was it?

01:00:47.542 --> 01:00:49.142
Where was it written?

01:00:49.142 --> 01:00:52.721
You saw it in pictures?

01:00:52.721 --> 01:00:55.592
Reply : In the scriptures.

01:00:55.592 --> 01:00:59.171
[unclear: Pentecost Side B 27:53].

01:00:59.171 --> 01:01:03.211
He sent out twelve men to do his work.

01:01:03.211 --> 01:01:04.211
Shri Mataji: Yes, it's all right.

01:01:04.211 --> 01:01:05.211
Now, I'll tell you what.

01:01:05.211 --> 01:01:06.211
You see, hot air will come out of everybody's
head now.

01:01:06.211 --> 01:01:07.211
Even you are sitting here.

01:01:07.211 --> 01:01:08.252
Because there is heat within you.

01:01:08.252 --> 01:01:11.352
First the hot air will come out.

01:01:11.352 --> 01:01:15.941
You see, Christ tried to give them realization
but they didn't believe Him.

01:01:15.941 --> 01:01:19.192
Believe me that they never believed Him till
he got His resurrection.

01:01:19.192 --> 01:01:21.451
No, till they got His resurrection you see.

01:01:21.451 --> 01:01:28.142
Till He got his resurrection, they were still
like this you see, little half baked, not

01:01:28.142 --> 01:01:29.142
fully there.

01:01:29.142 --> 01:01:31.062
And that's why the hot air came out .

01:01:31.062 --> 01:01:36.242
You will see now, gradually as you'll settle
down in Sahaja Yoga, when you will be fully

01:01:36.242 --> 01:01:39.322
equipped, when your vibrations will flow well,
it will be cool breeze.

01:01:39.322 --> 01:01:41.182
Otherwise, hot air comes out.

01:01:41.182 --> 01:01:43.372
You see, with people who have...

01:01:43.372 --> 01:01:46.481
most of you will first have hot air, no doubt
about it because there is heat within you.

01:01:46.481 --> 01:01:53.171
Now, I will tell you people very frankly about
it that when it is hot, say for example take

01:01:53.171 --> 01:01:56.382
Helium, Helium is a gas - you know that.

01:01:56.382 --> 01:02:02.432
When it is hot, all the molecules in it fight
within, revolt against each other.

01:02:02.432 --> 01:02:03.732
They are absolutely volatile.

01:02:03.732 --> 01:02:08.621
But when it cools down, they become collective
and they move in a collective way.

01:02:08.621 --> 01:02:11.971
Even in science it has been shown and it is
the cool breeze of the Holy Ghost which has

01:02:11.971 --> 01:02:13.512
been described in the Bible also.

01:02:13.512 --> 01:02:19.862
So it should be a cool breeze because even
the Apostles that Christ had, they did not

01:02:19.862 --> 01:02:21.742
get their realization fully because they were
doubting Him.

01:02:21.742 --> 01:02:26.802
Not doubting, I would say they did not have
that faith till they saw He was resurrected.

01:02:26.802 --> 01:02:31.562
And after resurrection to have faith was rather
wrong, isn't it?

01:02:31.562 --> 01:02:34.592
Untimely, I should say.

01:02:34.592 --> 01:02:37.622
I can understand that.

01:02:37.622 --> 01:02:39.981
That time, you see, this was not there.

01:02:39.981 --> 01:02:44.671
I mean, to talk of realization itself in that
country was something so out of the blue.

01:02:44.671 --> 01:02:49.882
They were fishermen, not Cambridge students,
and you could not explain to them.

01:02:49.882 --> 01:02:54.062
But still they were simple people and they
were honest, no doubt about it.

01:02:54.062 --> 01:02:59.112
But to their honesty, they could not understand
how... what this man is saying about self-realization

01:02:59.112 --> 01:03:00.492
or of second birth, you see.

01:03:00.492 --> 01:03:02.492
And so they doubted - was all right at that
time.

01:03:02.492 --> 01:03:08.921
But today it is not all right because once
you get realization, you see for yourself.

01:03:08.921 --> 01:03:09.921
All right?

01:03:09.921 --> 01:03:17.142
Q: [Unclear: also had this experience after
the resurrection Side B 30:10]

01:03:17.142 --> 01:03:20.772
Shri Mataji: You see, they had faith with
Him.

01:03:20.772 --> 01:03:25.942
But I wouldn't say they got realization, except
for John, I would say; but others, I am not

01:03:25.942 --> 01:03:26.942
very sure.

01:03:26.942 --> 01:03:31.981
Because the way they write about His works,
it's something an outsider writes, you see.

01:03:31.981 --> 01:03:34.962
It's just a ... not a person who is innate.

01:03:34.962 --> 01:03:37.072
You see, when they write, that's not there,
I find.

01:03:37.072 --> 01:03:40.192
But the worst of all I feel is about St. Paul
who should not be there at all.

01:03:40.192 --> 01:03:41.902
He had nothing to do with Christ.

01:03:41.902 --> 01:03:45.622
I can't understand why he is there because
according to Sahaja Yoga standard, he was

01:03:45.622 --> 01:03:47.332
a supra-conscious personality.

01:03:47.332 --> 01:03:50.431
I don't know why he put them there because
he saw a cross or he did all this.

01:03:50.431 --> 01:03:54.582
He was the one who was killing all the Christians
to begin with and then suddenly, I don't know

01:03:54.582 --> 01:03:58.872
how - it was a Roman trick perhaps to put
him there - I don't know why but somehow I

01:03:58.872 --> 01:04:00.362
cannot explain it.

01:04:00.362 --> 01:04:05.562
[Interruption by an audience - UNCLEAR Side
B 31:01]

01:04:05.562 --> 01:04:08.812
No, that's not the experience.

01:04:08.812 --> 01:04:10.772
Experience is different.

01:04:10.772 --> 01:04:12.752
The experience you can get it.

01:04:12.752 --> 01:04:15.402
You see, the other day only one lady saw a
cross on me.

01:04:15.402 --> 01:04:17.352
She saw auras.

01:04:17.352 --> 01:04:20.832
Another one saw something else; that's not
the thing.

01:04:20.832 --> 01:04:24.461
That's not reality.

01:04:24.461 --> 01:04:26.902
Q: You are saying his experience did not exist
but yours is existing.

01:04:26.902 --> 01:04:28.872
Shree Mataji: Yes, because that you can also
