01:04:30.312 --> 01:04:33.242
Anybody is taking LSD, they come and see Me.

01:04:33.242 --> 01:04:35.902
They just see lights coming out of Me.

01:04:35.902 --> 01:04:37.892
They don't see Me at all.

01:04:37.892 --> 01:04:39.552
