All right?

01:04:43.592 --> 01:04:44.592
Now leave it.

01:04:44.592 --> 01:04:49.042
You come and see Me, we'll talk about it.

01:04:49.042 --> 01:04:51.961
You see, we should see what have we got out
of it.

01:04:51.961 --> 01:04:55.992
All these discussions and these dogmas - what
have you got?

01:04:55.992 --> 01:05:00.882
You see, what are we going to achieve out
of it?

01:05:00.882 --> 01:05:03.292
Just think of it.

01:05:03.292 --> 01:05:05.702
What is the use?

01:05:05.702 --> 01:05:06.702
You have to get the reality.

01:05:06.702 --> 01:05:07.702
Why discuss all these things?

01:05:07.702 --> 01:05:10.852
We have so many clergies here who have been
studying Bible and all that and they are now

01:05:10.852 --> 01:05:11.852
fed up.

01:05:11.852 --> 01:05:12.852
Their heads are off now.

01:05:12.852 --> 01:05:15.661
This dogma, that dogma, this, that - it's
over now.

01:05:15.661 --> 01:05:16.661
Finish it.

01:05:16.661 --> 01:05:18.682
Just get the reality first then we'll talk
about it.

01:05:18.682 --> 01:05:19.682
All right?

01:05:19.682 --> 01:05:21.522
You just get the reality, then.

