So all of us should forget all about these
things.

01:10:11.701 --> 01:10:14.092
Be honest to yourself and fair to yourself.

01:10:14.092 --> 01:10:17.052
So far, by doing all these things you haven't
found yourself.

01:10:17.052 --> 01:10:18.671
Accept this fact.

01:10:18.671 --> 01:10:22.801
I have nothing to gain out of you.

01:10:22.801 --> 01:10:28.971
I haven't even written a single line, a book,
nothing.

01:10:28.971 --> 01:10:33.221
So you must know that it is your own.

01:10:33.221 --> 01:10:38.161
I am just like a banker who is cashing your
checks.

01:10:38.161 --> 01:10:44.051
Better have them cashed, for which you don't
have to pay anything.

01:10:44.051 --> 01:10:46.321
You don't have to put in any effort, nothing.

01:10:46.321 --> 01:10:49.891
But once you are realized then you will know
what is to be done.

01:10:49.891 --> 01:10:51.611
But first get your lights on.

01:10:51.611 --> 01:10:57.742
All right, now just co-operate with me as
I tell you, without much questioning.

01:10:57.742 --> 01:11:05.592
I am not going to tell you anything horrid
nor am I going to trouble you by anything.

01:11:05.592 --> 01:11:07.316
It is your own blessing just waiting at your
door step.

01:11:07.316 --> 01:11:08.316
Can you believe Me now?

01:11:08.316 --> 01:11:09.316
If you can believe only this much that I am
genuine, it will work out.

01:11:09.316 --> 01:11:10.316
May God bless you.

01:11:10.316 --> 01:11:11.316
All right, now put your hands towards Me and
if it is not very inconvenient, please take

01:11:11.316 --> 01:11:12.316
out your shoes because this Mother Earth also
helps us.

01:11:12.316 --> 01:11:13.316
It's better to take out your shoes; it helps.

01:11:13.316 --> 01:11:14.316
If you are sitting on the ground, it's all
right.

01:11:14.316 --> 01:11:15.316
You have to touch your Mother Earth with your
feet so if you can take out your shoes easily,

01:11:15.316 --> 01:11:16.316
it will work out faster.

01:11:16.316 --> 01:11:17.316
Moreover, it is a very tight thing on the
feet.

01:11:17.316 --> 01:11:18.316
Now this is the question of language of hands
which is an international language always,

01:11:18.316 --> 01:11:19.316
but this is the language where the hands get
enlightened and the hands have to speak.

01:11:19.316 --> 01:11:20.316
As Mohammad Sahib has said it clearly, "At
the time of resurrection, your hands will

01:11:20.316 --> 01:11:21.316
speak".

01:11:21.316 --> 01:11:22.316
So, your hands have to speak and that's how
we have to see how our hands will be speaking.

01:11:22.316 --> 01:11:23.316
So these centers which are shown here are
represented in your fingers.

01:11:23.316 --> 01:11:24.316
So, these are five, six and seven, this side
left and right.

01:11:24.316 --> 01:11:25.316
Once these centers are enlightened, then you
can feel yourself and feel others.

01:11:25.316 --> 01:11:26.316
To begin with, we do not understand what it
is because it is too great a thing.

01:11:26.316 --> 01:11:27.316
But once we start using it, we are amazed
how we start transforming, how things start

01:11:27.316 --> 01:11:28.316
happening to us.

01:11:28.316 --> 01:11:29.316
All right, now just put your hands straight
like this.

01:11:29.316 --> 01:11:30.316
Sit comfortably.

01:11:30.316 --> 01:11:31.316
Be comfortable.

01:11:31.316 --> 01:11:32.316
If you have anything tight, please make it
a little loose.

01:11:32.316 --> 01:11:33.316
It's better.

01:11:33.316 --> 01:11:34.316
Not that it makes any difference; it's very
subtle.

01:11:34.316 --> 01:11:35.316
But why I am asking you because attention
goes there if it is something tight.

01:11:35.316 --> 01:11:36.316
On the waist also if there is something tight
you see the attention is gone.

01:11:36.316 --> 01:11:37.316
Make yourself comfortable.

01:11:37.316 --> 01:11:38.316
That's the main point, be comfortable so that
for a while you could be with yourself comfortably.

01:11:38.316 --> 01:11:39.316
If you are wearing any big malas and all that,
please take it out.

01:11:39.316 --> 01:11:40.316
It's better.

01:11:40.316 --> 01:11:41.316
It's heavy.

01:11:41.316 --> 01:11:42.316
Anything like that, please take it out.

01:11:42.316 --> 01:11:43.316
It will help us.

01:11:43.316 --> 01:11:44.316
Just first get yourself realized and then
you start understanding.

01:11:44.316 --> 01:11:45.316
Now, after this I have to tell you one more
thing that you have to keep your eyes shut.

01:11:45.316 --> 01:11:46.316
The reason is that when the Kundalini rises
above this which it wants to pierce through,

01:11:46.316 --> 01:11:47.316
at that time it presses this point and the
pupils go into dilatation first before it

01:11:47.316 --> 01:11:48.316
is piercing it and that's why, if the eyes
are open and the Kundalini is passing through,

01:11:48.316 --> 01:11:49.316
She may stop.

01:11:49.316 --> 01:11:50.316
So please keep your eyes shut, that's all.

01:11:50.316 --> 01:11:51.316
Just keep your eyes shut till I tell you to
open them.

01:11:51.316 --> 01:11:52.316
And if you have spectacles and all that, you
can also keep them safe because you don't

01:11:52.316 --> 01:11:53.316
have to see Me anymore till I ask you to open
your eyes.

01:11:53.316 --> 01:11:54.316
So it's better to keep so that you don't have
problems of your spectacles.

01:11:54.316 --> 01:11:55.316
Now close your eyes.

01:11:55.316 --> 01:11:56.316
Now don't open your eyes as I requested you.

01:11:56.316 --> 01:11:57.316
Please don't open your eyes, that's all.

01:11:57.316 --> 01:11:58.316
Because this is just the opposite of hypnosis.

01:11:58.316 --> 01:11:59.316
In hypnosis, they make you open your eyes
and put their eyes into your eyes and do all

01:11:59.316 --> 01:12:00.316
these things.

01:12:00.316 --> 01:12:01.316
What's happening?

01:12:01.316 --> 01:12:02.316
Now, no gesticulations, nothing abnormal has
to be done.

01:12:02.316 --> 01:12:03.316
Whatever has to happen will happen within.

01:12:03.316 --> 01:12:04.316
Nothing abnormal thing has to be done.

01:12:04.316 --> 01:12:05.316
Nobody has to jump, shout or scream - that's
all nonsense.

01:12:05.316 --> 01:12:06.316
You are not to do anything like that, not
to turn your necks or anything.

01:12:06.316 --> 01:12:07.316
Just keep quiet.

01:12:07.316 --> 01:12:08.316
If you cannot keep quiet, it's better that
you go out for the time being.

01:12:08.316 --> 01:12:09.316
But just keep quiet.

01:12:09.316 --> 01:12:09.323
That's very important not to disturb others.
